data.description: $10,000 price reduction!!  This well maintained three bedroom, two full bath home has incredible views showcasing the post and beam accents in the great room which add such charm to the knotty pine tongue and grooved ceiling. Beautiful solid wood doors are accented by a wood detail. The kitchen is spacious with custom concrete counter tops, stainless steel appliances, wet bar, wine fridge, and pantry/mud room.  Master bedroom has a ton of square footage for office or reading nook. 3 car garage gives you room for parking toys or a workshop area. Come take a look at what this home has to offer.  This is a Bawcom built home, so you know the quality is there!
